{"tid":1181254,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意飲喜茶嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-01T12:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T16:39:58.000Z","uid":153905,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9761c1c037643ce7809f07c3c9de3d33d39839e","tid":1181254,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"今舖城大編委串到啲喜茶狗應一應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喜茶logo拎住八酒六四<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靚抽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKevzuG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKevzuG.jpg&h=898e39ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVhtk86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVhtk86.jpg&h=21fec119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【六四特刊第三十期】<br />\n<br />\n近年不少香港人頻頻北上飲喜茶，「喜茶」可說是當今中國經濟發展成功的象徵和産物。但在香港人追捧內地文化的同時，又會否仍記得中國今天的經濟成果，背後是基於一場屠殺？香港人還能夠認清打壓我們香港民主自由的敵人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n今年的六四特刊本報以城大師生角度出發，探討三大問題：<br />\n1. 六四被忘?<br />\n2. 支聯會六四晚會為何被唾棄?<br />\n3. 在「建設民主中國」上香港人被freeride?<br />\n<br />\n《六四特刊第三十期》網上版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HIaRjH8FYc4xEidhxI_y8h97b_VpxJEh/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1HIaRjH8FYc4xEidhxI_y8h97b_VpxJEh%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=26182139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HIaRjH8FYc4xEidhxI_y8h97b_VpxJEh/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n六月四日晚本報將到銅鑼灣派發刊物。"},{"pid":"402cef61c83580f0c7425fd1a53c367afa50c2ab","tid":1181254,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"八油六四"},{"pid":"56d4808f35c685813e37205c4c041852e6dab641","tid":1181254,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:42:58.000Z","msg":"喜茶狗唔上水?